Package org.opengis.openoffice

Interface XReferencing

  • All Superinterfaces:
    XInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Referencing
    public interface XReferencing
extends XInterface
    Services from the org.opengis.referencing package to be exported to OpenOffice.org. This interface is derived from the XReferencing.idl file using the javamaker tool provided in OpenOffice SDK, and disassembling the output using the javap tool provided in Java SDK. This source file exists mostly for javadoc purpose and in order to keep IDE happy. The .class file compiled from this source file must be overwritten by the .class file generated by javamaker.
    Since:
    3.1
